{"name":"Final Act","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"class":"NPC","schemaVersion":"1.01","notes":"<p>When reduced to 0 HP, your NPC can immediately perform some sort of special action or attack. Self-destructing robots and exploding fire <strong>elementals </strong>are great classics.</p>\n<p>Take some liberty with this Skill, making it powerful but also a hindrance for the NPC's allies. If this skill deals damage, it should be <strong>minor</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":0,"max":0},"isHeroic":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KwdjuchaeyZS9Ure"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.5.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679419388467,"modifiedTime":1679433275304,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"_id":"TNRcmQ7FL9hFLTyD"}
{"name":"Use Equipment","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"class":"NPC","schemaVersion":"1.01","notes":"<p>Your NPC gains one <strong>accessory</strong> slot, one <strong>armor </strong>slot, one <strong>main hand</strong> slot, and one <strong>off-hand</strong> slot. <strong>Soldier </strong>enemies should only be equipped with Basic Items; <strong>elite </strong>and <strong>champion </strong>adversaries, on the other hand, should often use Rare Items. If an NPC loses a weapon they have equipped, any Skills assigned bo the corresponding basic attack should be transferred to their <strong>unarmed strikes</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":0,"max":0},"isHeroic":false},"effects":[{"label":"Grant Equipment","icon":"icons/svg/aura.svg","origin":"Item.MOChutnzAYpzT4js","disabled":true,"_id":"0GEr3WB5mBaKSnvl","changes":[{"key":"system.canUseEquipment","mode":5,"value":"true","priority":null}],"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{}}],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.MOChutnzAYpzT4js"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.5.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679433025914,"modifiedTime":1679433298873,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"_id":"W6iJK4sP2BHz8VCL"}
{"name":"Crisis Effect","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"class":"NPC","schemaVersion":"1.01","notes":"<p>As long as they are in <strong>Crisis</strong>, your creature gains a special benefit or ability.</p>\n<p>Examples are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your NPC's damage Affinities change.</li>\n<li>Damage dealt by your NPC ignores Resistances (or maybe even Immunities).</li>\n<li>One or more of your NPC's <strong>attacks </strong>gain <strong>multi (2)</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Since this Skill will only activate when the creature is severely damaged, it's okay for the effects to be quite strong.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":0,"max":0},"isHeroic":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KT8FdosxrrtVA8EV"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.5.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679419172593,"modifiedTime":1679433273530,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"_id":"dpVakAHRdJOwBXEd"}
